docs.abstract: Netflix and Amazon are driving a small bump in the market for TV shows after a major slowdown.
docs.snippet: Netflix and Amazon are driving a small bump in the market for TV shows after a major slowdown.
docs.lead_paragraph: It has been nearly seven months since Hollywood resolved its strikes, but momentum still hasn’t taken hold in the entertainment industry. “Survive till ’25” has become an informal slogan among entertainment workers.

headline.main: Signs of Life Appear in TV Show Purchases
headline.print_headline: Netflix and Amazon Are Fanning Some Life Into the Moribund TV Show Market

docs.abstract: The Amazon Labor Union has been divided over strategy and governance issues after winning a representation vote at a Staten Island warehouse in 2022.
docs.snippet: The Amazon Labor Union has been divided over strategy and governance issues after winning a representation vote at a Staten Island warehouse in 2022.
docs.lead_paragraph: A dissident group has won control of the Amazon Labor Union, the only union in the country that formally represents Amazon warehouse workers, election results on Tuesday showed.

headline.main: Dissident Group Wins Amazon Union Leadership Vote
headline.print_headline: New Union Leaders Elected at Amazon Warehouse
